      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 19.62,
      "time_str": "00:19.620",
      "text": "又到凤凰花朵开放的时候",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 28.49,
      "time_str": "00:28.490",
      "text": "想起某个好久不见老朋友",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 35.66,
      "time_str": "00:35.660",
      "text": "记忆跟着感觉慢慢变鲜活",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 43.02,
      "time_str": "00:43.020",
      "text": "染红的山坡道别的路口",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 49.81,
      "time_str": "00:49.810",
      "text": "青春带走了什么留下了什么",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 56.92,
      "time_str": "00:56.920",
      "text": "剩一片感动在心窝",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 64.79,
      "time_str": "01:04.790",
      "text": "时光的河入海流",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 70.89,
      "time_str": "01:10.890",
      "text": "终于我们分头走",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 74.6,
      "time_str": "01:14.600",
      "text": "没有哪个港口",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 78.38,
      "time_str": "01:18.380",
      "text": "是永远的停留",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 81.08,
      "time_str": "01:21.080",
      "text": "脑海之中有一个凤凰花开的路口",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 89.07,
      "time_str": "01:29.070",
      "text": "有我最珍惜的朋友",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 97.31,
      "time_str": "01:37.310",
      "text": "也许值得纪念的事情不多",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 106.56,
      "time_str": "01:46.560",
      "text": "至少还有这段回忆够深刻",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 113.86,
      "time_str": "01:53.860",
      "text": "是否远方的你有同样感受",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 120.91,
      "time_str": "02:00.910",
      "text": "成长的坎坷分享的片刻",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 127.7,
      "time_str": "02:07.700",
      "text": "当我又再次唱起你写下的歌",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 134.49,
      "time_str": "02:14.490",
      "text": "仿佛又回到那时候",
      "translation": null
